title: NZ incoming PM, Chris Hipkins says he wants to go out and find you if you haven’t been vaccinated, page 1
cleaned_text:
Everyone will have an opportunity to get the vaccine, everyone will. 

 

 Sounds like New Zealand has a WEF winner for PM now. 

 

 twitter.com... 

 

 New Zealand’s incoming PM, Chris Hipkins says he wants to go out and find you if you haven’t been vaccinated The way this guy is talking, they want to go find, chase, and force vaccinations. See the video below...Everyone will have an opportunity to get the vaccine, everyone will.Sounds like New Zealand has a WEF winner for PM now. 





At this point I think it must be obvious to most that the vaccine is more important than Covid. Still trying to push it when its efficacy is zero and its side effects dramatic should show people that it has another purpose. TPTB are going to fry. 







 

 It's really disgusting what "leaders" will say. I want to say these dolts are out of touch, but they aren't. They know exactly what they're doing. Pharma is big business, and it wouldn't surprise me the slightest if these dolts are in the pocket of Big Pharma. 

 

 Look at media in general, they deny anything wrong with the Covid vaccinations and push it like you're a hero for taking it. Same with all the world leaders. All the time while ignoring any dangers from it. 

 

 This isn't being out of touch, this is pushing a dangerous substance for a reward. I'm no anti-vaxxer, I've had all mine (minus the covid shot). But seeing how the greater health community shrugged and even silenced those who disagreed lends me to believe those against it were right. 

 

 Truth can stand to be challenged, lies cannot.
